{
  "name": "TFU Partnership Template",
  "description": "Together for Ukraine Partnership Proposal Template - Copy and customize for new partners",
  "template": "partnership",
  "design_system": "tfu",
  "validate_tfu": true,
  "client": "REPLACE_ME_CLIENT_NAME",
  "data": {
    "title": "REPLACE_ME Partnership Proposal",
    "subtitle": "REPLACE_ME: Partnership subtitle or tagline",
    "organization": "The Educational Equality Institute",
    "partner": "REPLACE_ME_PARTNER_NAME",
    "overview": {
      "mission": "REPLACE_ME: Explain TEEI's mission and the partnership context",
      "value_proposition": "REPLACE_ME: Explain what this partnership will achieve",
      "impact": "REPLACE_ME: Describe the expected impact and outcomes"
    },
    "programs": [
      {
        "name": "REPLACE_ME: Program 1 Name",
        "description": "REPLACE_ME: Program 1 description",
        "students_reached": 0,
        "success_rate": "0%",
        "certification_rate": "0%"
      },
      {
        "name": "REPLACE_ME: Program 2 Name",
        "description": "REPLACE_ME: Program 2 description",
        "students_reached": 0,
        "success_rate": "0%",
        "certification_rate": "0%"
      },
      {
        "name": "REPLACE_ME: Program 3 Name",
        "description": "REPLACE_ME: Program 3 description",
        "students_reached": 0,
        "success_rate": "0%",
        "placement_rate": "0%"
      }
    ],
    "metrics": {
      "students_reached": 0,
      "countries": 0,
      "partner_organizations": 0,
      "certifications": 0
    },
    "call_to_action": {
      "headline": "REPLACE_ME: CTA Headline",
      "description": "REPLACE_ME: CTA description text",
      "action": "REPLACE_ME: Action text (e.g., Schedule a Partnership Discussion)",
      "contact": {
        "name": "Henrik Røine",
        "email": "henrik@theeducationalequalityinstitute.org",
        "phone": "+47 919 08 939"
      }
    }
  },
  "content_sources": {
    "content_json": "data/REPLACE_ME-partnership.json",
    "content_markdown": "deliverables/REPLACE_ME-Partnership-Content.md"
  },
  "output": {
    "formats": ["indd", "pdf_print", "pdf_digital"],
    "intent": "print",
    "filename_base": "TEEI-REPLACE_ME-Partnership-TFU",
    "export_path": "./exports",
    "pdf_settings": {
      "print": {
        "preset": "PDF/X-4:2010",
        "color_space": "CMYK",
        "resolution": 300,
        "bleed": "3mm",
        "crop_marks": true
      },
      "digital": {
        "preset": "High Quality",
        "color_space": "RGB",
        "resolution": 150,
        "optimize_web": true
      }
    }
  },
  "quality": {
    "validation_threshold": 140,
    "auto_fix": false,
    "strict_mode": true,
    "required_checks": [
      "tfu_compliance",
      "typography_design",
      "pdf_structure",
      "content"
    ]
  },
  "tfu_requirements": {
    "page_count": 4,
    "primary_color": "#00393F",
    "forbidden_colors": ["#BA8F5A"],
    "required_fonts": ["Lora", "Roboto"],
    "forbidden_fonts": ["Roboto Flex"],
    "required_elements": [
      "TFU badge (blue + yellow)",
      "Partner logo grid (3×3)",
      "Full teal cover page",
      "Full teal closing page",
      "Light blue stats sidebar",
      "Two-column program matrix"
    ]
  },
  "tfu_rules": {
    "require_logo_grid": true,
    "require_tfu_badge": true,
    "allow_flexible_metrics": false
  },
  "qa_profile": {
    "use_tfu_certification": true,
    "visual_baseline_id": "REPLACE_ME-tfu-v1"
  },
  "notes": [
    "========================================",
    "HOW TO USE THIS TEMPLATE",
    "========================================",
    "",
    "1. COPY this file to a new file named after your partner:",
    "   example-jobs/tfu-[partner-name]-partnership.json",
    "",
    "2. REPLACE all instances of 'REPLACE_ME' with actual values:",
    "   - CLIENT_NAME: Partner's display name (e.g., 'Google', 'Microsoft')",
    "   - PARTNER_NAME: Full partner organization name",
    "   - Partnership content: title, subtitle, programs, metrics, CTA",
    "   - File paths: content_json, content_markdown, filename_base",
    "   - visual_baseline_id: Unique ID for visual regression baseline",
    "",
    "3. CREATE content files:",
    "   - data/[partner-name]-partnership.json (copy structure from data/partnership-aws-example.json)",
    "   - deliverables/[Partner]-Partnership-Content.md (optional long-form content)",
    "",
    "4. GENERATE layout:",
    "   - Option A: Run python create_tfu_partnership_from_json.py --content-json data/[partner]-partnership.json",
    "   - Option B: Edit scripts/generate_tfu_from_json.jsx and run in InDesign",
    "",
    "5. VALIDATE:",
    "   - python validate_document.py exports/TEEI-[Partner]-Partnership-TFU-PRINT.pdf --job-config example-jobs/tfu-[partner]-partnership.json --strict",
    "",
    "6. CERTIFY:",
    "   - Ensure TFU certification criteria met (score ≥ 140/150, all CRITICAL checks pass)",
    "   - Record results in TFU-MIGRATION-STEP-7-FINAL-VERIFICATION.md",
    "",
    "========================================",
    "TFU CERTIFICATION REQUIREMENTS",
    "========================================",
    "- Scoring threshold: 140/150 (93%+)",
    "- Page count: Exactly 4 (not 3, not 5)",
    "- Primary color: Teal #00393F (NO gold #BA8F5A)",
    "- Fonts: Lora + Roboto (NOT Roboto Flex)",
    "- Required elements: TFU badge, logo grid, full teal cover/closing",
    "",
    "========================================",
    "OPTIONAL: TFU_RULES CUSTOMIZATION",
    "========================================",
    "The 'tfu_rules' section allows per-partner flexibility:",
    "- require_logo_grid: Set to false if partner doesn't have 9 logos",
    "- require_tfu_badge: Set to false if non-TFU variant (not recommended)",
    "- allow_flexible_metrics: Set to true if metrics section differs",
    "",
    "Note: Changing these may affect TFU certification status."
  ]
}
